{"word":"Horse","slug":"horse","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Horse</b> Description of:<br/> - Great strength<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=39&verse=25'>Job 39:25</a> <br/> - Swifter than eagles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=4&verse=13'>Jer 4:13</a> <br/> - Snorting and neighing of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=28'>Isa 5:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=8&verse=16'>Jer 8:16</a> <br/> - A vain thing for safety<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=33&verse=17'>Psa 33:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=21&verse=31'>Pro 21:31</a> <br/> Used by, in war:<br/> - The Egyptians<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=14&verse=9'>Exo 14:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=15&verse=19'>Exo 15:19</a> <br/> - The Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=4'>1Ki 22:4</a> <br/> Used for cavalry<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=18&verse=23'>2Ki 18:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=47&verse=3'>Jer 47:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=51&verse=21'>Jer 51:21</a><br/> Egypt famous for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=31&verse=1'>Isa 31:1</a><br/> Forbidden to kings of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=17&verse=16'>Deu 17:16</a><br/> Hamstrung:<br/> - By Joshua<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=6'>Jos 11:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=9'>Jos 11:9</a> <br/> - By David<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=4'>2Sa 8:4</a> <br/> Israel reproved for keeping<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=2&verse=7'>Isa 2:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=31&verse=1'>Isa 31:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=15'>Eze 17:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=14&verse=3'>Hos 14:3</a><br/> Exported:<br/> - From Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=10&verse=29'>1Ki 10:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=25'>2Ch 9:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=9&verse=28'>2Ch 9:28</a> <br/> - From Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2&verse=66'>Ezr 2:66</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=7&verse=68'>Neh 7:68</a> <br/> Bits for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=59&chapter=3&verse=3'>Jas 3:3</a><br/> Bells for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=14&verse=20'>Zec 14:20</a><br/> Harness for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=46&verse=4'>Jer 46:4</a><br/> Color of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=1&verse=8'>Zec 1:8</a><br/> Commerce in<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=18&verse=13'>Rev 18:13</a><br/><a href='S:Horse, Exported'>Horse, Exported</a> <br/> Dedicated to religious uses<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=23&verse=11'>2Ki 23:11</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=1&verse=8'>Zec 1:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=6&verse=8'>Rev 6:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=9&verse=17'>Rev 9:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=66&chapter=19&verse=21'>Rev 19:21</a>"}]}